Class PdfDashPattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lowagie.text.pdf.PdfObject

  • public class PdfDashPattern
extends PdfArray
    A PdfDashPattern defines a dash pattern as described in the PDF Reference Manual version 1.3 p 325 (section 8.4.3).
